(60357, 169633, 0, 1, 'The Last Breath - Borderline', '中文翻譯:\r\n\r\n你說你的生命正在墜落\r\n你想就這麼自我了結\r\n我能像你一樣有勇氣嗎？\r\n因為我所背負的只有罪孽\r\n\r\n告訴我它馬的能得到什麼\r\n在我經歷過這些以後\r\n而我又該承認嗎?\r\n“你只是被這些藥迷失在痛苦中”？\r\n\r\n想就這樣扣下扳機\r\n來結束我的痛苦\r\n"帶我去看你去過的地方"\r\n我用顫抖的聲音說著\r\n\r\n這一切已經失控\r\n在上帝將我離棄的黑暗中淌著血\r\n請來這裡幫助我\r\n\r\n從一開始，我是那麼的相信\r\n我就快要觸摸到天空\r\n但當我回過頭看這一生\r\n我卻一直站在這個只再多走一步就會崩潰的邊緣\r\n\r\n我應該停止在這裡，或邁出這一步呢？\r\n我應該就這麼繼續做自己嗎？\r\n我知道這條路是獨自一人要走下去的\r\n但我累的無法再走了，你可以帶走我的一切嗎？\r\n\r\n我不是你想像的那個人\r\n無法掩飾我的痛苦\r\n但我會盡力試著去飛\r\n即使我的翅膀離我很遠\r\n我知道這是很難相信\r\n但這就是我的一切\r\n即使你們有一天會離開這裡\r\n我仍會繼續唱下去\r\n\r\n我會繼續唱下去！\r\n\r\n從一開始，我是那麼的相信\r\n我就快要觸摸到天空\r\n但當我回過頭看這一生\r\n我卻一直站在這個只再多走一步就會崩潰的邊緣\r\n\r\n但我這次不會停在這了，也不會短暫的停留\r\n因為我選擇繼續做自己\r\n我知道這些傷痛是必須獨自一人承受的\r\n但我會將這一切放下的\r\n你願意為我而停留嗎？', '2013-02-03 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '(A1)\r\nYou''ve said you''re life''s fallin''\r\nYou wanna kill yourself\r\nCan I get the same of your courage?\r\nCuz what I''ve only carried is GUILT.\r\n\r\nTell me WTF can I get after I''ve made it through?\r\nShould I commit by these: "You''re only suffering by those pills."?\r\n\r\n(A2)\r\nWanna pull the trigger\r\nTo end my misery\r\nShow me what you''ve been\r\nThrilling with my voice\r\nIt''s outta control\r\nBleeding in the shadow\r\nWhere god has forsaken me\r\nPlease help me in here\r\n\r\n(C)\r\nFrom the very start, I was so convinced\r\nI''m about to touch the sky\r\nBut when I look back of my life\r\nThere''s only one step left of my borderline\r\n\r\nShould I stop right here or just take the leap?\r\nShould I just be who I am?\r\nI know this road is all alone\r\nBut I''m so tired to go, will you take me away?\r\n\r\n(B)\r\nI am not the man you think\r\nCan''t take the pain behind my face\r\nBut I''ll try to fly, even my wings are far away from me.\r\nI know this is hard to believe\r\nBut it is everything to me\r\nEven most of you will leave this place\r\nI will still sing\r\n\r\nI WILL STILL SING!!\r\n\r\n(C)\r\nFrom the very start, I was so convinced\r\nI''m about to touch the sky\r\nBut when I look back of my life\r\nThere''s only one step left of my borderline\r\n\r\nI won''t stop right here or just take the brief\r\nI will just be who I am\r\nI know this wound is all alone\r\nBut I will let this go, so will you stay with me?', '', 264, '', 'The Last Breath', 'Will', 'The Last Breath', '無', '', 0, 1, 1, '2013-02-03 22:16:58', '2013-10-07 17:23:53', '2013-06-23 18:41:31'),
